item.description: Hello, I am Jixin Gao, received the M.S. degree in control science and engineering from Harbin Engineering University, Qingdao, China. I am currently pursuing the Ph.D. degree in mechanical engineering at Harbin Institute of Technology, Harbin, China. My research interests include state estimation, multi-sensor fusion SLAM, and robot navigation system.
